data.description: Welcome Home!! There is so much to love about this charming 3BD/1.5BA 2 story home.  This beauty is situated on a corner lot and boast such features as: Large covered front porch, rich hardwood floors, lovely main entry, replacement windows, main level laundry, open kitchen, and full useable basement.  Outside, there's a paved parking area and patio, right next to the 2 car garage!  Classic Style, Comfort, Character and Affordability all wrapped into one!!   Make it yours today!
